# CDOC

## Introduction

- The backend is a [NestJS + Typescript](https://nestjs.com/) monorepo use a microservices structure where there is a main API that provides data to the frontend, a service that consumes emails and populates a database and a service that extracts data from Greendocs.

- The frontend is a [Vite + ReactJS + Typescript](https://vite.dev/) project, managing sessions and exposing features such as analysis and management of centralized data, generation of reports, graphs, etc.

## Dependencies

- [Docker + Docker Compose](https://www.docker.com/get-started/)
- [VSCode](https://code.visualstudio.com/download)
- [Node](https://nodejs.org/pt/download)

## Setup

1. Install all dependencies
2. Clone repository with command `git clone https://github.com/oppemsolutions/cdoc.git`
3. Open repository using VSCode and install dependencies with command `yarn install`

## Creating Docker images

To compile the projects you can use the command's below:

- **Backend - Api**

  ```ps
  docker build \
    --no-cache \
    --file ./backend/Dockerfile \
    --build-arg APP_NAME="api" \
    --tag "cdoc/backend/api" .
  ```
  
- **Backend - Email Importer**

  ```ps
  docker build \
    --no-cache \
    --file ./backend/Dockerfile \
    --build-arg APP_NAME="email-importer" \
    --tag "cdoc/backend/email-importer" .
  ```

- **Backend - Greendocs Extractor**

  ```ps
  docker build \
    --no-cache \
    --file ./backend/Dockerfile \
    --build-arg APP_NAME="greendocs-extractor" \
    --tag "cdoc/backend/greendocs-extractor" .
  ```

## Running projects

To run the projects, it is necessary to pass all the environment variables on which each project is dependent. Dependencies will trigger errors if they do not have the environment variables declared.

- **Backend - Api**

  ```ps
  docker run \
    --rm \
    --network cdoc \
    -e LIBS_DATABASE_URL="postgres://postgres:postgres@postgres:5432/postgres" \
    -e LIBS_CACHE_URL="redis://redis:6379/0" \
    -e LIBS_STREAM_URL="redis://redis:6379/1" \
    -e LIBS_QUEUE_REDIS_URL="redis://redis:6379/2" \
    "cdoc/backend/email-importer"
  ```

- **Backend - Email Importer**

  ```ps
  docker run \
    --rm \
    --network cdoc 
    -e LIBS_DATABASE_URL="postgres://postgres:postgres@postgres:5432/postgres" \
    -e LIBS_CACHE_URL="redis://redis:6379/0" \
    -e LIBS_STREAM_URL="redis://redis:6379/1" \
    -e LIBS_QUEUE_REDIS_URL="redis://redis:6379/2" \
    "cdoc/backend/email-importer"
  ```

- **Backend - Greendocs Extractor**

  ```ps
  docker run \
    --rm \
    --network cdoc \
    -e LIBS_DATABASE_URL="postgres://postgres:postgres@postgres:5432/postgres" \
    -e LIBS_CACHE_URL="redis://redis:6379/0" \
    -e LIBS_STREAM_URL="redis://redis:6379/1" \
    -e LIBS_QUEUE_REDIS_URL="redis://redis:6379/2" \
   "cdoc/backend/greendocs-extractor"
  ```

```mermaid

    class Role {

    class Profile {
```
